snippet.title: FRENZIES EARLY ACCESS LAUNCH TRAILER | OUT NOW | META QUEST 2, 3 & PRO
snippet.description:
The arena doors are being blown open! FRENZIES is now in Early Access, and you can play it for FREE! 

Step into the neon-drenched arenas and fight your way through a medley of chaotic round types. Embrace your teammates and then turn enemies in the ultimate showdown as you strut your way to proving who's really No.1 - all while looking fresh as ****. Think you've got what it takes? 

Conquer the chaos, rise to the top, and embrace your worst self this October. 

The king of VR shooters from nDreams Studio Near Light will be only be on Meta Quest during Early Access. Play now: https://bit.ly/3YbGKUK

FRENZIES will be coming PS VR2 at full launch. 

Follow the chaos on FRENZIES socials: 
Discord: https://discord.gg/frenziesvr
X: @frenziesvr
TikTok: FrenziesVR
